title: New Royal Enfield Bullet 350 launched in India, prices start at Rs 1.73 lakh
description: Royal Enfield has launched the 2023 Bullet 350, with prices starting at Rs 1.73 lakh. The bike comes with new features such as a 349cc engine, new headlight and taillight, and a digital-analogue instrument cluster. It is available in three variants, with the top-spec variant featuring a blacked-out engine. The Bullet 350 will compete with the Honda H'ness CB350 and the Jawa Forty Two. Bookings are now open, and deliveries will begin from September 3, 2023.
